causal_map:
Fourier transform of g(x, y) → Fourier transform of g(x, y) + e^{kx}; 
                    e^{kx} → Laplace correction term; 
                    Laplace correction term → Fourier transform of g(x, y) + e^{kx}; 
                    Fourier transform of g(x, y) + e^{kx} → result inside the domain; 
                    Laplace correction term → result inside the domain; 
                    g(x, y) → Fourier transform of g(x, y); 
                    e^{kx} → Fourier transform of e^{kx}
